'''同性婚姻'''在[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]没有得到承认。2011年和2012年，[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]政府曾尝试在新起草的宪法中添加对[[LGBT|LGBT]]人群包容性的语言。然而，在2012春季各政治派别之间的谈判失败，临时宪法的实施被搁置，直到举行新的选举。

2015年9月16月制宪议会批准新宪法<ref>{{Cite news|title = Assembly in Nepal Approves New Constitution|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/17/world/asia/assembly-in-nepal-approves-new-constitution.html|newspaper = The New York Times|date = 2015-09-16|access-date = 2015-09-17|issn = 0362-4331|first = Bhadra|last = Sharma|archive-date = 2015-09-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150920102232/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/17/world/asia/assembly-in-nepal-approves-new-constitution.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，新法中包括涉及LGBT人群权利的若干规定，但并没有解决[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]的问题。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title = Nepal lawmakers approve first LGBTI protections in new constitution - Gay Star News|url = http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/nepal-lawmakers-approve-first-lgbti-protections-in-new-constitution/|accessdate = 2015-09-17|date = 2015-09-15|archive-date = 2019-12-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191213214933/https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/nepal-lawmakers-approve-first-lgbti-protections-in-new-constitution/|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
2008年11月17日，尼泊尔最高法院裁决法律充分保障LGBT人群和所有被法律定义为“自然人”的少数性别人群权利，这包括结婚的权利。“这是一个对性少数群体里程碑式的决定，我们对此表示欢迎。”尼泊尔首个公开的同性恋议员和[[南亚|南亚]]领先的同性恋权利活动家Sunil Babu Pant说。<ref>[http://pewforum.org/news/rss.php?NewsID=17001 Nepal's Supreme Court OKs same-sex marriage] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207001716/http://pewforum.org/news/rss.php?NewsID=17001 |date=2008-12-07 }}</ref>法院要求政府成立一个委员会来研究其他国家的同性伴侣关系的法律和规定，新的法律不歧视性少数群体，包括[[反串|反串]]和[[跨性别|跨性别]]。<ref>[http://www.365gay.com/news/nepal-supreme-court-orders-full-lgbt-rights/ Nepal Supreme Court orders full LGBT rights] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100205133034/http://www.365gay.com/news/nepal-supreme-court-orders-full-lgbt-rights/ |date=2010-02-05 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?sectionName=&id=7c190914-f498-427c-ad0b-97559a3aae71&&Headline=Nepal+SC+approves+same-sex+marriage Nepal SC approves same-sex marriage] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205134941/http://www.hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?sectionName=&id=7c190914-f498-427c-ad0b-97559a3aae71&&Headline=Nepal+SC+approves+same-sex+marriage |date=2008-12-05 }}</ref>

2009年3月22日，印度亚洲新闻社采访Pant时他说：“尽管法院批准同性婚姻，但政府尚未制定法律，”同性婚姻法案尚待起草或表决，更不用说立法。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pinknews.co.uk/news/articles/2005-12106.html |title=Gay Nepalese MP looks towards greater acceptance of gays and lesbians |access-date=2015-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111021135423/http://www.pinknews.co.uk/news/articles/2005-12106.html/ |archive-date=2011-10-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2009年6月，Pant说：“这个过程才刚刚开始，尼泊尔正在经历转型期，一切似乎都在缓慢地前进。七人组成的委员会已成立并开始工作，研究其他国家同性婚姻法案。希望他们能尽快起草一份同性婚姻法的建议，并将其交给政府批准。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.starobserver.com.au/soap-box/2009/06/16/progress-in-new-republic-of-nepal/13887 |title=Progress in new republic of Nepal |accessdate=2015-11-11 |archive-date=2020-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314174243/https://www.starobserver.com.au/opinion/soapbox-opinion/progress-in-new-republic-of-nepal/13887 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

一些消息来源报导说，同性婚姻和保护性少数群体将被纳入尼泊尔正在起草的新宪法。<ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/News-Feed/nepal/Nepal-charter-to-grant-gay-rights/Article1-499154.aspx Nepal charter to grant gay rights] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100123144431/http://www.hindustantimes.com/News-Feed/nepal/Nepal-charter-to-grant-gay-rights/Article1-499154.aspx |date=2010-01-23 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/nepal/7027736/Nepal-to-stage-gay-weddings-on-Everest.html |title=Nepal 'to stage gay weddings on Everest' |accessdate=2015-11-11 |archive-date=2015-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016144836/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/nepal/7027736/Nepal-to-stage-gay-weddings-on-Everest.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

尼泊尔目前的临时宪法规定了制宪议会负责编写尼泊尔永久宪法。根据临时宪法的规定，新宪法2011年11月30日对外公布<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/xinhua/2011-08-12/content_3482031.html Nepali interim Constitution to be amended for extension of CA term]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，但这个期限后来延长六个月，到2012年5月31日。

2012年5月28日关于新宪法的谈判失败，总理解散制宪会议筹备新的选举。<ref>{{cite web |last=Narayan |first=John |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-18234114 |title=Nepal enters crisis mode as constitution talks fail |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=2012-05-28 |accessdate=2014-04-05 |archive-date=2013-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215102734/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-18234114 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其结果是，同性婚姻的未来仍不确定。

2013年11月19日进行制宪议会选举。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-24987573 |title=Nepal voting ends for new Constituent Assembly |accessdate=2018-12-23 |archive-date=2018-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311103825/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-24987573 |dead-url=no }}</ref>这次投票被一再推迟<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_asiapacific/view/1259799/1/.html |title=Channel NewsAsia |publisher=Channel NewsAsia |date= |accessdate=2013-11-24 |archive-date=2013-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130315083834/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_asiapacific/view/1259799/1/.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，早先已计划于2012年11月22日之后的制宪会议于2012年5月27日解散，由选举委员会推迟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/News-Feed/nepal/Nepal-fails-to-meet-constitution-deadline/Article1-862113.aspx |title=Nepal fails to meet constitution deadline |publisher=Hindustan Times |date= |accessdate=2012-05-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528122025/http://www.hindustantimes.com/News-Feed/nepal/Nepal-fails-to-meet-constitution-deadline/Article1-862113.aspx |archivedate=2012-05-28 }}</ref>2014年2月10日[[苏希尔·柯伊拉腊|苏希尔·柯伊拉腊]]当选为总理，打破政治僵局并对宪法最终敲定。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/11/world/asia/nepal-ends-long-stalemate-in-picking-prime-minister.html?_r=0 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-11-11 |archive-date=2014-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309084853/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/11/world/asia/nepal-ends-long-stalemate-in-picking-prime-minister.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年1月，研究同性婚姻的国际法律和准备报告此事的政府委员会成员表示，除由委员会主席起草的总结外报告的工作已基本完成。主席承诺将该报告在一个月之内提交给政府，但他说，内阁对此事不感兴趣。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ekantipur.com/the-kathmandu-post/2014/01/22/top-story/report-on-same-sex-marriage/258435.html |title=Report on same-sex marriage |access-date=2015-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029221739/http://www.ekantipur.com/the-kathmandu-post/2014/01/22/top-story/report-on-same-sex-marriage/258435.html |archive-date=2014-10-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2014年8月，[[美联社|美联社]]报道说，该委员会已决定建议同性婚姻合法化。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lgbtqnation.com/2014/08/nepals-lgbt-community-parades-for-same-sex-marriage/ |title=Nepal’s LGBT community parades for same-sex marriage |accessdate=2015-11-11 |archive-date=2016-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504011745/http://www.lgbtqnation.com/2014/08/nepals-lgbt-community-parades-for-same-sex-marriage/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>该委员会于2015年9月将报告提交给政府。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/nepal-panel-recommends-legalising-same-sex-marriage/article1-1315512.aspx |title=Nepal panel recommends legalising same sex marriage |accessdate=2015-11-11 |archive-date=2015-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150729001547/http://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/nepal-panel-recommends-legalising-same-sex-marriage/article1-1315512.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.news24.com/World/News/Nepal-committee-calls-for-legalising-same-sex-marriage-20150210 |title=Nepal committee calls for legalising same-sex marriage |accessdate=2015-11-11 |archive-date=2019-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217074043/https://www.news24.com/World/News/Nepal-committee-calls-for-legalising-same-sex-marriage-20150210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年8月，该国的法律，司法，制宪议会和议会事务部长表示他的部下将提出法案合法化同性婚姻。如果国会通过该法案也将使尼泊尔成为亚洲第一个允许同性婚姻的国家。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://scroll.in/article/674232/Nepal-to-legalise-homosexuality-and-same-sex-marriages,-says-law-minister |title=Nepal to legalise homosexuality and same-sex marriages, says law minister |accessdate=2015-11-11 |archive-date=2019-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190207235453/https://scroll.in/article/674232/Nepal-to-legalise-homosexuality-and-same-sex-marriages,-says-law-minister |dead-url=no }}</ref>

